{"word":"ἐμπάζομαι","slug":"ἐμπάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπάζομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:perhaps'>perh.</a> from <el>ἔμπαιος</el>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to busy oneself about, take heed of, care for</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a><a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; once <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a>\n"}]}